source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Management Question J4:  Where are aquatic/riparian areas with potential to change from climate change?
source.description: This map shows naturalized flow change for April-July for 3 periods: 1951-1965 (historic), 2016-2030, and 2046-2060 simulated by the Bureau of Reclamation across 112 GCM scenarios.
